### List all badges
GET http://localhost:8080/api/badges
Accept: application/json


### Get badge by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/badges/1
Accept: application/json

### Create badge (without key, should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/badges
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hero",
  "description": "Brave supporter",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/hero.png"
}

### Create badge
POST http://localhost:8080/api/badges
X-API-Key: dev-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hero",
  "description": "Brave supporter",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/hero.png"
}

### Update badge (without key, should fail)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/badges/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Badge",
  "description": "Updated desc",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/new.png"
}

### Update badge
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/badges/1
X-API-Key: dev-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Badge",
  "description": "Updated desc",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/new.png"
